FBIS4-43505 "drweu117_i_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-117 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 FRANCE Announces Opening of Aid Route Announces Opening of Aid Route LD1606221494 Paris Radio France International in French 2100 GMT 16 Jun 94 LD1606221494 Paris Radio France International French BFN [Text] We have just received a communique from the Foreign Ministry, announcing the opening of a humanitarian corridor to Kigali. The route will be open from Saturday 18 June to transport 30 tonnes of emergency aid to the Rwandan capital. According to the Foreign Ministry communique, the first convoy will leave the Ugandan border for Kigali on Saturday morning.
